Boca Juniors won the championship in this round with the following line-ups:

Ferro Carril Oeste (BA) Gualco;
                   Noseda, Garavano;
                                Pont, Corvetto, Vázquez;
                                                Natino, Páez, Benítez Cáceres, Pérez, Danza.

Boca Juniors            Vacca;
                                Marante, Valussi;
                                                Sosa, Lazzatti, Pescia;
                                                                Boyé, Corcuera, Sarlanga, Varela, Sánchez.

Referee                 Cossio.

Field:                  Ferro Carril Oeste.

Att.:                   31.000 tickets.

80' 0-1 Sarlanga.
87' 0-2 Sarlanga.

Champion: Club Atlético Boca Juniors.


